{"items": [{"shortCode": "DZDBKOIjkfF", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DZDBKOIjkfF/", "caption": "A recent cleaning company settlement is a reminder that getting customers matters, but how you market matters too.\n\nIf you're advertising a special offer, make sure pricing, memberships, cancellation policies, and terms are clear from the start. Short-term wins from misleading marketing can lead to long-term problems.\n\nTrust is built through transparency, not fine print.", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T14:48:29.000Z", "videoDuration": 112.546, "videoPlayCount": 449, "videoViewCount": 198, "likesCount": 19, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/711802528_841498591940809_3961826962298066642_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gERiiUsTVFNC0E6UrvewI7e8KMusnRoMfLbCY6DIDlqUjRFQq4Tu1zKgH4dYXm7EAg&_nc_ohc=ZlZ0rgfcCkgQ7kNvwG4G4FG&_nc_gid=-nwIMG3frkrm4OnB0Q6ljQ&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_MIQsFarCdhOe-jgfN444jKC02PU83irhau09nSSfthA&oe=6A312EF9&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQOoTIVjdi3suU7voLczZjwjTHY6Bmn0z2s2ltFmnwiZ_ta-o5wdalHcDiBKHGIkljVcJQzaQ1qYB7KZQ65bx80g4i6H8MSm3tWSCOE.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=107&vs=1549245253492267_2247337249&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC85QjQ3QjA1QkRCRUI1NDZEMERCODkwQzFBMUI5NTg5Ql92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyL0M4NDk4OUFGQ0U4MkFDQ0QyNUUyQzNCMjMzMjVCMzg4X2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAmvIr%2B2vWBy0AVAigCQzMsF0BcItDlYEGJGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=0f453d0966&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-TegeX2jgVYn9V8411j1kDWLxpFa25BkL8qapokAkeWA&oe=6A2D3CF4&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26280241558317942"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "DY94JxdkSMR", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DY94JxdkSMR/", "caption": "Freedom in business isn\u2019t about doing everything yourself. Real freedom comes from creating systems, automation, and processes that allow your business to run without depending on you every second. If you have to answer every message, solve every problem, and handle every task alone, you don\u2019t own a business, you own a job. Automation, delegation, and structure create consistency, save time, reduce stress, and give you the ability to actually grow.", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T14:53:34.000Z", "videoDuration": 68.6, "videoPlayCount": 82, "videoViewCount": 23, "likesCount": 2, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-dfw6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/712115849_18179127154396446_4341441400037568502_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-dfw6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH0czSeyaIQrt_7AKNwEEJ3opUKyUp362H2VOwDKZB3Nf2Eir97c_9DNoI5lIjwpeg&_nc_ohc=Te5NWThW8cYQ7kNvwEvxtYV&_nc_gid=isU_ImXtgft3CosNL-QJAw&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af9qVVHWymLs5WDLh9y-GyDohvHY1nvQbzsNeL16re-VWw&oe=6A311362&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-dfw6-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQPH1rf_SrCg0fJ3lGm5vHj5JD58fsj1chFVF7pnWKn8C302a--xy8jpNTHO5HZWdBgas4X2uCQFRkCF9MGBBFA8Q1sKOGcVyKTLYnE.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=103&vs=1854137461947454_3832247865&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=bc6586729e&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af_Vk4qe6rEIfptw-ErsDcEhcJUUdPx5HhONFwSrnEgbHA&oe=6A2D44AF&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "36516065747991917"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "DY4uPT-jK0A", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DY4uPT-jK0A/", "caption": "You\u2019re probably not losing clients because of your price. You\u2019re losing them because of poor follow up. Most customers don\u2019t expect perfection, they expect communication. Replying late, forgetting leads, not checking back in, and inconsistent communication will cost you more money than raising your prices ever will. A lot of business owners blame the market, but the real problem is leads going cold because nobody stayed consistent enough to close them.", "timestamp": "2026-05-28T14:50:29.000Z", "videoDuration": 96.479, "videoPlayCount": 65, "videoViewCount": 19, "likesCount": 2, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.fhnl3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/709770790_18178908577396446_2790896922723274108_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.fhnl3-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH0ZFaKam5nvasOi65TWsgfa5htK2DfJHGUHTHoiVcpbQh-lC6stBdwiWu6LQQreHA&_nc_ohc=5m6HNG6Xo1IQ7kNvwGDcAiy&_nc_gid=HhbLvWPSFqHykCpfDho97w&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af-EUaGjwXfRxfeD5C4IbbXbOx0Fg5FOeW8h8SEHm3-neA&oe=6A3112C4&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://instagram.fhnl3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQNcG1UfwvWJXz8l9ZUA__W7y4JV5NPUfb32I_vF3qrf-EGeHgt0ac8cFX8f1DwJzP44au2ErMYsD2IBnV1fc8mojobPTg6E_rCuVwc.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=105&vs=18178908544396446_76724301&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=0605e50517&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-gE7RGOPzFT72MiEJ-ek3y1K_1ubWalXtZ-LxoyuZ_VQ&oe=6A2D4B9B&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26852217957780984"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "DY2JE93DRPZ", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DY2JE93DRPZ/", "caption": "Most business owners don\u2019t need more motivation, they need leadership. Avoiding hard conversations, lacking systems, failing to follow up, avoiding accountability, and being inconsistent will always cost you money and opportunities. Growth comes from handling problems directly, communicating clearly, and staying consistent even when it\u2019s uncomfortable. The small things you avoid today usually become the bigger problems hurting your business tomorrow.", "timestamp": "2026-05-27T14:47:37.000Z", "videoDuration": 37.675, "videoPlayCount": 62, "videoViewCount": 22, "likesCount": 0, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/709067139_18178803451396446_873908212755319550_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEqiYBrP47HA84ekrb3m-71zj3el7_TRpaK5bFNCZ_3l_lYxCgVP3tmKOzSx1GvrY4&_nc_ohc=98edTpzwJDsQ7kNvwF6OlZU&_nc_gid=5gQqEeR8gTEnJzD0Og95Xw&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_BOaLKwExf1bTb3plw_Tg0njpwCsfjyHMMz7K4a6d5fw&oe=6A3113EF&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQOl7bEiw6mRoHK_cIs1cQ9mKW3gOJXMUpZqANfBIJ4zflojAR_U5yZ2tpaAMTXA6KO3UPx7B_zqxBfOY833a3a5FjNoK7kuLclfqv8.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=101&vs=1281973817250979_3176354748&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC81MzQzMjI2ODg2ODY1MTFDN0FERUM3Rjc1NzVEODVCQV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzg5NEIwRThFM0VEOTg1QjUxNkVGOTFFREVGRkFFQzk5X2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAmvKys1c%2FhykAVAigCQzMsF0BC1T987ZFoGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=8d2844ce3e&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af9Qrnv77EFvMgPz-Lhd2zEMsurqFNDApGbe_g2y_uoTRg&oe=6A2D22C7&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27274039688951253"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "transcript": "Here we go again. Your business does not need more motivation right now. It needs leadership because some of y'all are avoiding the very things that will grow your business. You want an example? Avoiding hard conversations, avoiding systems, avoiding follow-ups, avoiding accountability, avoiding consistency, and that avoidance is costing you clients, money, and opportunities. Entrepreneurship will expose every weak area in your life. That's right, I said it. And inside of Tenacity Academy, we teach real entrepreneurship, structure, discipline, marketing, systems, leadership, and execution. Comment ready if you're ready to grow for real.", "hook_type": "Contrarian", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "DYw_eiTDdkf", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYw_eiTDdkf/", "caption": "A logo, colors, and a clean brand won\u2019t save your business if you lack discipline. If you don\u2019t follow up, reply late, show up inconsistently, or fail to keep your word, you\u2019ll still struggle. Branding helps people recognize you, but discipline is what keeps customers coming back. Most businesses don\u2019t fail because of bad logos, they fail because of inconsistency, poor communication, and lack of work ethic. Reliability will always beat aesthetics.", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T14:47:27.000Z", "videoDuration": 37.174, "videoPlayCount": 65, "videoViewCount": 15, "likesCount": 0, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-mia3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/708304436_18178581211396446_736341710866666891_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE6L-On7Mt_jMC0KZ2iAjXuyPo2XIG7tKQTJ4XKA70S7WSiJ9aX_60fQnWXp13cl_g&_nc_ohc=EIsk_NjF4qsQ7kNvwELmNyT&_nc_gid=FNj6IYWyGWuIoc_0r8WcQA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af9kAzQQujoWIr4kU4c8_GdLWPHNRZRqbIE1nJ3pOL--zA&oe=6A312BE0&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-iad3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQPbYVf0hOoDTLydt8oofhY2Ie3hb8XT_wmYuK2_Yvlx2BQsDozgASO6nU-ijpB_2yJTzcCQIOYNk2zqgzHJ1Tiyjo4Ho8RTSiauv8g.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=111&vs=969121389076512_3921937093&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=464b7ebd7e&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af8ggRqOd0VWXYP9N4nL3U0hcpro91jSBAxsOVO8ZTm2Kg&oe=6A2D343A&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "35609427085371247"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "transcript": "So listen up, I might step on a few toes today, so I don't even care. But some of y'all don't need another logo, you need discipline because a beautiful brand will not save a disorganized business. Yep, you can have all the colors, the best photos, the best websites, but if your follow-up is weak, baby listen, your systems are messy and your execution is inconsistent. You are still going to struggle, struggle, struggle. But inside of Tenacity Academy, we focus on what really grows businesses like systems, structure, leadership, marketing, automation, and execution. So comment, execute if you're serious about growth and join our community. Click that link down below.", "hook_type": "Contrarian", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "DYrxUncCL8a", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYrxUncCL8a/", "caption": "Running a cleaning business isn\u2019t always as glamorous as social media makes it look.\n\nSome months are slow.\nSome clients drain your energy.\nAnd being \u201cbusy\u201d doesn\u2019t always mean you\u2019re making money.\n\nOne thing I learned:\nBurnout usually comes from lack of systems, not hard work.\n\nThe businesses that last aren\u2019t built on motivation alone\u2026\nthey\u2019re built on consistency, structure, and the right team around you.", "timestamp": "2026-05-23T14:07:35.000Z", "videoDuration": 21.133, "videoPlayCount": 579, "videoViewCount": 283, "likesCount": 33, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/705423832_18178350613396446_2394542089313434548_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGIQtczxmoJiWncjX69upBSC_dHpLy0OLwBmI0Y0Ndz7ffhHSe9FwO5A9_WJtF0Vto&_nc_ohc=N_Ltn_YkCy8Q7kNvwEWwpYa&_nc_gid=vGsRTO1XfaMvbPsa_F8Mlw&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af-Cxo-YqRuFDEAAltTPaa0tyHLi8C5f4T5KYf2HYf4dkA&oe=6A3131D6&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQOrR5eaVxoX22cbsJJCclSYAcBNNqfPAJwD7rP1Aqpf65hbmtb2eOPk3nzH5jOZTsn-ir4rLQXZsjlyfmFUMqqc2K0MaFRnkAcG73g.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=109&vs=2464821260698743_548620933&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=4153eb2b7d&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-IJ5MwZGbxzQPRJZirvD12oTd6Xy7Vdap6g6GKR6CA7g&oe=6A2D36CB&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26734024716218893"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "transcript": "Sometimes the loud is badder, ain't outside the door. It's the one inside my mind. Feel got a voice. Stuck on a script and some days it feels like they're both talking at the same time. I deal through them with my fists.", "hook_type": "Personal Experience", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "DYpM6ZdleFy", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYpM6ZdleFy/", "caption": "A lot of people think you need experience, degrees, or a huge investment to start a business.\n\nTruth is, many successful service businesses started with basic equipment, consistency, and learning as they went.\n\nThe biggest mistake? Waiting until you \u201cfeel ready.\u201d\n\nMost of these businesses can start small and grow fast through referrals, social media, and good customer service.\n\nSometimes the opportunity you\u2019re looking for is simpler than you think.", "timestamp": "2026-05-22T14:10:20.000Z", "videoDuration": 17.133, "videoPlayCount": 352, "videoViewCount": 150, "likesCount": 10, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-phx1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/705305914_18178244194396446_1442256031126889254_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-phx1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHUvqT644SMcL--I-JXjg3OfJ-En_aI8lEr-QbmnJSQgVsarzqsN_g08PMXdyiDwts&_nc_ohc=vKoGBV3X0REQ7kNvwFBPIGi&_nc_gid=boRLww0XIW9nBRRtera3GA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_buWp2IQdgpJggzJ_bAzikSWYFOOrIC4Eyj1MuwzGZoQ&oe=6A3119DD&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-phx1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQPg2hPDlPzZLOgks4HPSTqj-jw_PuIG0H2O4Xvs2EaccLBWjER4OGqANV3S-7JXM_Q1YRpuOIXsdzmYffXFWHbN7awUtwhfZq25RLU.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=101&vs=2044833989711454_1823997218&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=cd9b194579&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af910djWc53tvLvyCIggZ-Mv9jSYUazwLOnx1Fig6o_sDQ&oe=6A2D1E39&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "Tenacity Academy", "song_name": "Candid Cleaning Conversations", "uses_original_audio": false, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "26428423046775376"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "is_relevant": true}, {"shortCode": "DYerhislbx2", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYerhislbx2/", "caption": "I used to think making money was the hard part. But keeping it, scaling it, and protecting your peace is a whole different skill.\n\n3 things changed my life:\n\n1. I stopped doing everything myself.\n2. I treated my business like a real business with systems and structure.\n3. I protected my time, health, and relationships.\n\nA lot of business owners are silently struggling behind the scenes. Growth means nothing if it costs you everything else.", "timestamp": "2026-05-18T12:06:47.000Z", "videoDuration": 31.433, "videoPlayCount": 471, "videoViewCount": 240, "likesCount": 17, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.flas1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/702240741_18177807811396446_2736996288102348283_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.flas1-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGs6BduKrL6YWV8QChhuIrZJsTEpAu5TfdsZxpCTHfR6DrDeJokxjN2kiK057Zfcyg&_nc_ohc=7bEIACsdD0IQ7kNvwEpBvoE&_nc_gid=_X27GoFlUHYzz1ft2AxkfA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_aGkctop7c6kVmwvWBJt4QLubtPuyEHeE3dJPNSrL5DA&oe=6A313E1C&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQNwGoeCtIQRIpBZ-O0v1A5RccZP4_GFJ4_hf8aq0xZc1VQfRI1mDusXojP8OG_enIXPYiJUm2DJM9vYprYlrzrDEoaD9TNH5X15HZA.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=103&vs=984037627358164_3080092145&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC84MDRBOTRDQkMxNkY1QTA0RUQ5MEFDMDA3OTU2QzNBMl92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzhCNEI2N0Y0Mjc0REJEREIyNkIzOUYzQUM4QkJGQzkzX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAm4q%2FCgd%2BI2z8VAigCQzMsF0A%2FbtkWhysCGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=89b91398e6&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af9mztp-ua7f8fkSmMIZbjEKC3aw6OdNmd85VxiukvWtlA&oe=6A2D4FE9&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "tenacityacademy", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27007605505559611"}, "ownerUsername": "tenacityacademy", "ownerFullName": "Cleaning Business Coach", "transcript": "Love the voice that I gave you, trying to build a future with you. Emotions involved, we called all day, every plan we had to look at mine. You put all on my shoulders, friends do some, got a whole thing, even off of more than I choose. They see the wings but they don't see my roots, and as I fade out with a million things on my mind. They don't see the pressure when the night runs low, they don't see the stress when the cash flow slow, they don't see the tears when the door don't close, but they really see I'm still standing.", "hook_type": "Personal Experience", "is_relevant": false}, {"shortCode": "DYcNJ48HQg8", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYcNJ48HQg8/", "caption": "Running a service business taught me that skill alone isn\u2019t enough.\n\nFast replies matter.\nFollow-ups matter.\nSystems matter.\nAnd the cheapest clients usually bring the biggest headaches.\n\nOne thing I learned too:\nContent builds trust before customers even contact you.\n\nA lot of business owners are talented\u2026\nbut struggle because they\u2019re missing structure, consistency, and communication.\n\nThese lessons would\u2019ve saved me a lot of time, stress, and money early on.", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T13:02:55.000Z", "videoDuration": 20.2, "videoPlayCount": 430, "videoViewCount": 215, "likesCount": 7, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-msp1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/702231548_18177704965396446_2844284978661128689_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-msp1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGc8BeFwbZnPgBGhOHwWkBQCzO8mFpSXxJpBDFKcQlfwzYwruzrHJyJbHu96hlSpbs&_nc_ohc=bi8-Qx54uLMQ7kNvwHLniPx&_nc_gid=4rtX4VdCpgIp09qLQ37zyA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af93juaYFyAX1_oJLFIJQJ3WcLySmJhhu_PYz2CHm7PH_A&oe=6A3131DE&_nc_sid=10d13b"